Title: Let the Seller Beware
Plot: Grissom and Catherine investigate the murder of a wealthy couple who are discovered outside  their glamorous home, which was up for sale. Sara probes the death of a cheerleader who is found eviscerated on a soccer field, her organs having been ingested by her killer.
GuestStars: Chris Payne Gilbert, Mary-Margaret Humes, Taylor Handley, Nicole Paggi, Laurie Fortier, Monique Demers, Edward Edwards, Peter Asle Holden, Chris Johnson, Michael McLafferty, Rachel Shumate, Kendra D. Smith, Mary
